00Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26bf0dc91c716d19ac1362671ddbc73835bcc15b","tid":857531,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e52f54bcdfc2bb90a9631473aa9fd95596f81495","tid":857531,"uid":55533,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"馬拉佬都有guts過港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n人地係國家"},{"pid":"93fa0976e9f4be1d41b318fa7f72b88a34bc80e7","tid":857531,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b54aa3d594d5af76d399c72c3fa2f66cfa4a141","tid":857531,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:41:48.000Z","msg":"今日馬拉<br />\n明日大嶼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ac7bdbecbc6c3d81497281d427ceab2c8d7bbb","tid":857531,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"中國周圍殖民好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56acf96636076ff6dbde14be1ae436bb8f3d6381","tid":857531,"uid":53705,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f9ac7bdbecbc6c3d81497281d427ceab2c8d7bbb","tid":857531,"uid":67816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"中國周圍殖民好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:13:16.000Z","msg":"最痴線係, 點解世界各國唔出兵打鳩中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明眼人都知道, 中共軍隊根本係紙老虎<br />\n上一次印度入侵中國邊境, 中共口交部 叫春叫左幾個月, 都唔敢還擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果世界各國好似印度咁, 一齊派兵入侵中國<br />\n保證中共即刻下跪道歉, 唔敢再周圍搞事<br />\n<br />\n根本中共越來越惡, 都是世界各國容忍佢"},{"pid":"ea59c0ea2d7195637a